title: Jella Haase
summary: Jella Haase (born 27 October 1992) is a German actress. She began acting in theatre at a very early age. Her film credits include Lollipop Monster, Fack ju Göhte and Combat Girls.  She has also appeared on the television shows Polizeiruf 110 and Alpha 0.7 – Der Feind in dir. She won the Bavarian Film Award for Best Young Actress in 2012, the Günter Strack Television Award in 2013 and earned a nomination at the German Film Awards in 2014.
